Description:
The Mission of Capital Region Building Owners and Managers Association (CRBOMA) is to nurture the growth and health of the local Commercial Real Estate Industry by:

representing, actively and responsibly, the interests of our members;
providing educational programs for the advancement of professionalism in the industry;
fostering communication and networking opportunities within the industry and the community; and,
disseminating information to our members from BOMA International and other reliable sources.

Jacobs Van der Meij, retail property agent for A1 locations with 35 years of experience.

The shopping streets in the 60 major cities are our playing field. The dynamics of the retail market our passion. Thinking in terms of possibilities for questions concerning retail property our challenge.

Whether the letting, renting, selling or buying of retail property is concerned, the result is what counts for us. Direct, clear and creative.

Based on our experience, we can therefore offer the following services:
•renting and letting of retail property in A1 locations;
•project-based letting of new shopping centres;
•conceptual advice for new buildings and redevelopment of shopping centres;
•acquisition and sale of retail chains;
•rent assessment;
•valuations;
•purchase and sale of individual shop premises and shopping centres;
•advice about financing and funding.

VISION
We believe in quality, not quantity. In being a niche player with perfect knowledge of the market. For us trust, expertise and a personal touch are paramount.

Siamo specializzati nella costruzioni di immobili e installazioni di pregio.

Inoltre ci occupiamo da anni dei servizi di post vendita anche per coloro che possiedono già un immobile:

Manutenzione, tenuta chiave della casa ed intervento h24 per qualsiasi emergenza;
Manutenzione impianti;
Manutenzione piscina;
Gestione affitti turistici;
Servizi di interior Design.

@Work Hubs, enables you to connect, network and grow your business. From our brand new co-working hub, we have the right infrastructure, environment and support services to suit your needs, whether you are a home-worker, mobile worker, entrepreneur or small business. The space is conveniently located just next to Eustion Station and is easy to use with memberships or hourly rates.

Within the hub you can choose to work from a desk, collaboration space, lounge, private room, meeting room or quiet space. In additon we have a kitchen, with great coffee and a selection of teas, lockers and printing facilities. Sitting at the same desk 9-5 all day every day reduces your productivity significantly.


'Liberating the way we work'

- Implantação de novas lojas do modelo "built-to-suit"(BTS) e locações tradicional;
- Prospecção de parceiros (empresas/lojistas) em expansão para sistema de real estate;
- Negociação comerciais e jurídicas;
- Prospecção, avaliação e venda de terrenos para incorporação;
- Prospecção, avaliação e venda de imóveis comerciais;
- Prospecção de novos negócios;
- Identificação e pontos comerciais para implantação de lojas no modelo "but for rental";
- Análise sobre taxas de retorno, estudo de viabilidade para implantação de novos empreendimentos comerciais;
- Administração e propriedades imobiliárias;
- Construção e imóveis para venda;

Créée en 2018, #FAMAG_SERVICES est spécialisé dans la ventes et la #distribution_exclusif des pièces détachées #SONALIKA, et autres,
